379
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:21,280
But when you were little...

380
00:19:21,810 --> 00:19:23,930
That was all in the past.

381
00:19:41,490 --> 00:19:42,050
Mom.

382
00:19:42,790 --> 00:19:43,640
I remember you used to

383
00:19:43,640 --> 00:19:46,050
