423
00:22:21,310 --> 00:22:21,790
Here.

424
00:22:22,030 --> 00:22:23,440
Good thing you're back.

425
00:22:24,940 --> 00:22:27,860
♪ Where did she go to play? ♪

426
00:22:28,300 --> 00:22:31,280
♪ I don't understand either ♪

