00:24:05,270 --> 00:24:06,200
You bought this?

450
00:24:07,880 --> 00:24:09,080
Someone gave it to me.

451
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:10,710
That's a lot.

452
00:24:15,280 --> 00:24:15,760
Here.

453
00:24:20,790 --> 00:24:22,250
